          "removeTopPadding": "false",
          "jcr:created": "Thu Jul 14 2022 03:16:19 GMT+0000",
          "headline2": "Get Answers",
          "theme": "white",
          "jcr:lastModified": "Thu Jul 10 2025 20:30:20 GMT+0000",
          "singleExpansion": "false",
          "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/expander",
          "textIsRich": "true",
          "item_1657754806454": {
            "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
            "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading D",
            "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/box",
            "content": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "fontFamily": "primary",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "scotton",
              "fontWeight": "thin",
              "as": "p",
              "text": "<p>A: Showcase is a beloved 10-inch collectible character created by Pop Mart that has become a cultural phenomenon. Many brides want custom Showcase event dresses to match their own gown as a unique keepsake, photo prop, or gift for their event party who also collect Showcase dolls.</p>\n",
              "align": "left",
              "color": "gray800",
              "uppercase": "false",
              "measure": "md",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Thu Jul 10 2025 20:20:41 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/content",
              "textIsRich": "true",
              "display": "block"
            }
          },
          "item_1657754838066": {
            "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
            "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading C",
            "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/box",
            "content": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "fontFamily": "primary",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "scotton",
              "fontWeight": "thin",
              "as": "p",
              "text": "<p>A: Custom Showcase event dresses start at $50, with companion and other outfit options starting at $35. Final pricing depends on the complexity of the design, fabric choice, and embellishments.</p>\n",
              "align": "left",
              "color": "gray800",
              "uppercase": "false",
              "measure": "md",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Thu Jul 10 2025 20:21:01 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/content",
              "textIsRich": "true",
              "display": "block"
            }
          },
          "item_1657754857377": {
            "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
            "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading D",
            "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/box",
            "content": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "fontFamily": "primary",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "scotton",
              "fontWeight": "thin",
              "as": "p",
              "text": "<p>A: Showcase dolls are approximately 10 inches tall. Our custom event dresses are precisely tailored to fit authentic Showcase proportions, ensuring a perfect fit for your original Showcase doll.</p>\n",
              "align": "left",
              "color": "gray800",
              "uppercase": "false",
              "measure": "md",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Thu Jul 10 2025 20:21:20 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/content",
              "textIsRich": "true",
              "display": "block"
            }
          },
          "item_1657754882477": {
            "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
            "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading C",
            "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/box",
            "content": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "fontFamily": "primary",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "scotton",
              "fontWeight": "thin",
              "as": "p",
              "text": "<p>A: Yes! Our designers can recreate virtually any event dress style in miniature, from classic ball gowns to modern minimalist designs, bohemian styles, and even colored event dresses.</p>\n",
              "align": "left",
              "color": "gray800",
              "uppercase": "false",
              "measure": "md",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Thu Jul 10 2025 20:21:37 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo-site-a/components/content",
              "textIsRich": "true",
              "display": "block"
            }
          }
        },
